The chatbot uses Microsoft's Azure system >e has problems like all artificial intelligences, which at the moment still fall in contradiction. Not all answers, generally, are accurate, but in the case of commercial activity the relapse of errors can be heavy, not only on the lives of the direct concerned, but also for legal reasons. In the meantime, a new warning appeared on the site in which it is reported that the robot "would provide sometimes non-accuracy or incomplete answers" and invite entrepreneurs to "not use its answers as legal or professional advice".
